name: Fishbone and One Eye
description:
This is my first artwork. I made this artwork on 22 July 2021. 
Why did I make this artwork? actually, I don't really know. sometimes my childhood memories pop up in my head. My Mama said I always draw so many fish on the wall but I can't remember it. so that memory is very blurry like look the sun with one eye, and the fish all gone just bones left.
